Sovereign Debt Risk Surges to Record in Europe, Swaps Show

-- B y   A b i g a i l   M o s e s
-- 
2011-07-11T07:35:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/sovereign-debt-risk-surges-to-record-in-europe-swaps-show.html
The cost of insuring sovereign debt
surged to a record with the Markit iTraxx SovX Western Europe
Index of credit-default swaps rising 15 basis points to 271,
according to index administrator Markit Group Ltd.  To contact the reporter on this story:
